flowchart TD
  START([invoke connectionId + fn + token]) --> RESOLVE[resolve connection + checksum integrity]
  RESOLVE --> EST{state established?}
  EST -->|no| NC[MeshRejected not_connected]
  EST -->|yes| IDP[identity propagation\nIdentity.resolve → context.identity]

  IDP --> SEC{security admission\nmutual identity + allowedSources + mtls}
  SEC -->|deny| V1[policy violation\nInvocationFailed · MeshRejected reason]
  SEC -->|allow| POL{Policy.evaluate?}
  POL -->|deny| V2[MeshRejected policy_denied]
  POL -->|allow / none| RL{rate limit policy?}
  RL -->|consume → blocked| V3[MeshRejected rate_limited]
  RL -->|allowed / none| TRAF{traffic maxConcurrent?}
  TRAF -->|exceeded| V4[MeshRejected traffic_limit]
  TRAF -->|slot| DISC{discovery port?}
  DISC -->|resolve endpoint| CTX
  DISC -->|none| CTX[build secure context\nsource · destination · endpoint · route · identity]

  CTX --> STARTED[InvocationStarted]
  STARTED --> RETRY{retryPolicy.resiliencePolicyId + Resilience port?}
  RETRY -->|yes| DELEG[Resilience.execute wraps fn\ntimeout-bounded]
  RETRY -->|no| DIRECT[run fn with timeout]
  DELEG --> OUT{ok?}
  DIRECT --> OUT
  OUT -->|resolved| DONE[record success + latency\nInvocationCompleted]
  OUT -->|threw / timeout| FAIL[record failure\nInvocationFailed]

  DONE --> END([result + route + latency · inflight--])
  FAIL --> END
  V1 --> END
